{"tid":1237250,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［150煙霧彈，5個暴動罪］點投訴一哥好？","createTime":"2019-06-17T14:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T15:49:18.000Z","uid":199120,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1d6d2d5f5087dbb84141d76c54001b978131accd","tid":1237250,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:11:38.000Z","msg":"我好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1，浪費公帑<br />\n2，指揮官判斷失誤<br />\n3，和平示威人士身心受到傷害<br />\n4，無理被捕人士身心受到嚴重傷害<br />\n5，分化警隊及其他政府機構<br />\n6，包庇警隊不合法情況下執法<br />\n7，包庇警隊不合法情況下獲得情佈<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我要無罪釋放所有義士<br />\n我要條撚皮道歉</span>"},{"pid":"739042102b4ad330589ced002897bcdb32d34a65","tid":1237250,"uid":174498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:13:20.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83a89213fc23e3d47d6ee9afd4b6e36a257f1bc","tid":1237250,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:15:26.000Z","msg":"係咪上街嘅人唔夠多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好以為可以係咁射走責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614cdc85f3896c503a4b73d69cb26ea270efaaa7","tid":1237250,"uid":57329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"仲投訴<br />\n起訴啦<br />\n香港又好 國際又好 起訴佢<br />\n邊個俾指示要搶搶打頭 亂棍圍扑倒地人士<br />\n對在場站立而無危險性嘅市民作武力攻擊<br />\n警員定係政府都係係法例之下  <br />\n我唔信咁多遊行人士揾唔到十個八個律師幫手 其他人提供片段証據 <br />\n搞個起訴政府及警員濫用武力委員會 我怕捐款多個東華三院籌款"},{"pid":"f365ec6b064e65c241a04338fd11a972f7ad7177","tid":1237250,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:23:52.000Z","msg":"pushhhhhh"},{"pid":"3ffea1cc1082e4e63a06d9cb837e85d4c338fb99","tid":1237250,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p